954
01:05:58,830 --> 01:06:00,999
Tarik napas kembali.

955
01:06:02,640 --> 01:06:04,439
Aku tidak bisa menang sekali pun.

956
01:06:05,540 --> 01:06:07,509
Aku berusaha sebaik mungkin,

957
01:06:08,509 --> 01:06:10,350
